<http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/PostAssertionNote/2966> rdfs:label "Post Assertion Note: #2966" ;
	a dprr:PostAssertionNote ;
	dprr:hasSecondarySourceForNote <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/SecondarySource/1> ;
	dprr:hasNoteType <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/NoteType/1> ;
	dprr:hasNoteText "Fast. Cap., Degrassi 52f., 124, 466f. (P. [C]ornelius [P. f. P. n. Scipio] African. Aimil., C. Livius M. Aimiliani f. M. [n. D]rusus); Fast. Ant., ib. 160f. (P. Cornel[i] S[- - - -], C. [- - - -]); Obseq. 20; Chr. 354; Fast. Hyd.; Chr. Pasc.; Cassiod.; and on Livius, Cic. Brut. 109; on Scipio, CIL 1\n     .2.763 c- Inscr. Ital. 13.3.71; ILS 8769, with NS 1935, 201f. Within the year Scipio brought the siege of Carthage into its final stages (Polyb. 38.7-8, and 20.2; Liv. Per. 51; App. Lib. 113-126; Flor. 1.31.13-15; Zon. 9.29-30; cf. Diod. 32.22). On the assignment of provinces between the Consuls, see App. Lib. 112; and cf. above, 148, on Scipio, Münzer, RE, on Livius." ;
	dprr:hasID 2966 .
